title: The Time Ring
body:
Remember when the Doctor said he only wanted a mate? well, he should have been careful what he wished for because it might have just come true.

Sorry

“I’m sorry for what’s happening to you, Amanda. The plan was not to get your brother involved. I just wanted to find her because I don’t know how much time we have.” Noli started, walking…

Read more…

summary: I had a dream that I was at some kind of wrap party for the Doctor Who Fiftieth Anniversary special with a group of people from...
body: I had a dream that I was at some kind of wrap party for the Doctor Who Fiftieth Anniversary special with a group of people from school and then I left and when I got in the car to leave David Tennant somehow called me and I told him I was at the party and he was trying to figure out how they’d let me in (in a very what-did-you-do-on-this-production way, not a you’re-not-supposed-to-be-here way) and I told him I wasn’t there anymore and like, halfway through explaining this my brain decided the party had been a dream so I panicked and hung up and then I woke up and realized both halves of the dream were the same dream
